name: Live PD
overview: Dash cams capture footage from urban and rural police forces while on the job. A live look inside the everyday calls of police officers across the nation.

episodes.overview: LIVE in six cities across America tonight, Friday October 28th, this program shows the actions and investigations of police forces across the country. Viewers will ride along in real time with six diverse police departments for a transparent look at law enforcement on duty.
This episode was cancelled due to a power outage.

episodes.name: Top 10 Animals on the Loose
episodes.overview: A countdown of the Top 10 animal encounters from A&E’s hit series “Live PD.”

episodes.name: Officers Look Back Live
episodes.overview: A new live special that looks at some of the most intense encounters from “Live PD” and features live in-studio interviews with the officers involved in the encounters.

episodes.name: Overtime - 05.01.19
episodes.overview: The pre-recorded third hour from the previous night’s (5/1/19) “Live PD.”

episodes.name: Wanted Live
episodes.overview: This live special will update the stories of the fugitives the “Live PD” audience has already helped capture while embedding live with task forces around the country as they serve warrants in real time.
